window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Assassins aren’t born. They’re forged.</b></p> <p>Before he became a vigilante assassin, a legend feared by criminals, Silence Jones’ previous life was stolen from him in one night - his fiancée murdered, his throat crushed, and his face destroyed.</p> <p>His brutal revenge leaves behind a long trail of mangled bodies, which captures the attention of a covert group hidden in plain sight within US government. The organization makes Silence an irresistible offer: If he joins their ranks as an assassin, they’ll lend their full support to his blood-soaked rampage.</p> <p>But when Silence discovers that the people who killed his fiancée have much bigger plans in mind - plans with deadly implications for national security - his mission suddenly shifts focus from vengeance to duty. A catastrophe is ready to explode, and the only person who can stop it is an untested assassin.</p> <p>The first stand-alone action thriller in the pulse-pounding new series. Enter the world of Silence Jones. Hold on tight…. If you like action heroes with the steely resolve of Lee Child’s Jack Reacher, the calculating will of Gregg Hurwitz’s Orphan X, and the raw power of Mark Greaney’s Gray Man, then you’ll love Silence Jones.</p> <p>Unlock <i>The Suppressor</i>, and start your Silence Jones mission today!</p>"; 
